Class AshwoodEntitySorter

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.objectstyle.cayenne.access.util.DefaultSorter
        |
        +--org.objectstyle.cayenne.map.AshwoodEntitySorter
All Implemented Interfaces:
DependencySorter, EntitySorter
public class AshwoodEntitySorter
extends DefaultSorter
implements EntitySorter

Implements dependency sorting algorithms for ObjEntities, DbEntities and DataObjects. Presently it works for acyclic database schemas with possible multi-reflexive tables. The class uses topological sorting from ASHWOOD library.

Since:
1.1
Author:
Andriy Shapochka, Andrei Adamchik
